---
title: One-Pot Venison, Beef & Mushroom Bolognese Gnocchi with Cherry Tomatoes & Parsley
description: Don’t tell the classic spag’ bol’ but pillowy gnocchi is taking over tonight. They are like delicious clouds that soak up the saucy beef and venison so well that it may be the new best way to have bolognese.
